---
title: Balsamic Onion and Ricotta Flatbreads with Garlic-Roasted Zucchini and Green Salad
description: This veggie-loaded flatbread is so filling and delicious, you won't miss the meat. Golden and garlicky zucchini, creamy ricotta as well tangy caramelized onions are all here for your veggielicious dinner that does not skimp on flavour!
